data.description: Look no further!  Check out this charming 3 bedroom, 2 full bath, 1 car garage Ranch home situated on .6 acre lot.  This home features an open concept, Living Room with vaulted ceilings, wood cabinetry, & huge closet space!  First floor laundry room with built in cabinets and counter space.  The lower level, with walkout access, is fully finished including a bedroom, full bath, living space, and lots of storage.  Do not miss out on this adorable home, schedule your showing today!
